data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this charming ranch-style home located in the desirable Summercrest neighborhood. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts a tasteful blend of updates throughout. Step into the inviting living area featuring a vaulted ceiling adorned with rustic beams and a white brick fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance. The galley kitchen is a chef's delight with large windows offering a  view of the expansive backyard. Retreat to the spacious primary suite and indulge in the updated bathrooms. Enjoy the serenity of a large backyard, making this home a true haven. Don't miss the chance to make this updated and inviting residence your own! Recent updates include: Dishwasher, Water Heater, AC, Roof, and flooring.
